org.araneaframework.framework.filter
Class StandardTransactionFilterWidget

java.lang.Object
  org.araneaframework.core.BaseComponent
      org.araneaframework.core.BaseService
          org.araneaframework.core.BaseWidget
              org.araneaframework.framework.core.BaseFilterWidget
                  org.araneaframework.framework.filter.StandardTransactionFilterWidget
All Implemented Interfaces:
Component, FilterWidget, java.io.Serializable, Service, TransactionContext, Widget
public class StandardTransactionFilterWidget
extends BaseFilterWidget
implements TransactionContext

Filters update(InputData), event(Path, InputData), process() and render(OutputData) based on the transaction id. If the transaction id is consistent, the mentionend actions get called on the child service, otherwise they do not.
